<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>WazeBR — Monitoramento de Tráfego em Tempo Real</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Plataforma de monitoramento de tráfego urbano em tempo real para órgãos públicos e concessionárias de rodovias. Alertas Waze, congestionamentos, chuva e muito mais.">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300..700&family=Syne:wght@600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        :root {
            --bg:        #0b0f14;
            --surface:   #111720;
            --surface-2: #161d28;
            --border:    rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
            --text:      #e8edf3;
            --muted:     #7a8799;
            --faint:     #3a4553;
            --accent:    #1d9cf0;
            --accent-2:  #0e7acc;
            --green:     #22c55e;
            --amber:     #f59e0b;
            --red:       #ef4444;
            --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            --font-display: 'Syne', sans-serif;
            --radius-sm: 6px;
            --radius-md: 10px;
            --radius-lg: 16px;
            --radius-xl: 24px;
        }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
        body {
            font-family: var(--font-body);
            background: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text);
            line-height: 1.6;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        img { display: block; max-width: 100%; }
        a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
        button { cursor: pointer; font: inherit; border: none; }

        /* ── NAV ── */
        nav {
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            height: 64px;
            background: rgba(11,15,20,0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }
        .nav-logo {
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
            font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: var(--text);
        }
        .nav-logo svg { color: var(--accent); }
        .nav-cta {
            background: var(--accent); color: #fff;
            padding: 8px 20px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600;
            transition: background 0.18s;
        }
        .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--accent-2); }

        /* ── HERO ── */
        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: clamp(6rem, 12vw, 10rem) clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem) clamp(4rem, 8vw, 6rem);
            position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .hero-glow {
            position: absolute; top: -20%; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 700px; height: 700px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(29,156,240,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .hero-badge {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
            background: rgba(29,156,240,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(29,156,240,0.25);
            color: var(--accent); border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 6px 16px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .hero-badge span { width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent); animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
        @keyframes pulse { 0%,100%{opacity:1} 50%{opacity:0.3} }
        .hero h1 {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 5rem);
            font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.05;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            max-width: 900px;
        }
        .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); }
        .hero p {
            font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.5vw, 1.2rem);
            color: var(--muted); max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.7;
        }
        .hero-actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center; }
        .btn-primary {
            background: var(--accent); color: #fff;
            padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            font-weight: 600; font-size: 1rem;
            transition: background 0.18s, transform 0.18s;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent-2); transform: translateY(-1px); }
        .btn-ghost {
            border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text);
            padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
            font-weight: 500; font-size: 1rem;
            transition: border-color 0.18s, background 0.18s;
        }
        .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--accent); background: rgba(29,156,240,0.05); }

        /* ── STATS BAR ── */
        .stats-bar {
            background: var(--surface);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 2rem clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        }
        .stats-grid {
            max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
            display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem; text-align: center;
        }
        .stat-val {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
            font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent);
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        }
        .stat-label { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px; }

        /* ── SECTIONS ── */
        section { padding: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 7rem) clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); }
        .section-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .section-tag {
            font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
            font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .section-sub {
            font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--muted);
            max-width: 540px; line-height: 1.7;
        }

        /* ── FEATURES ── */
        .features-grid {
            margin-top: 3.5rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5px;
            background: var(--border);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg); overflow: hidden;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background: var(--surface); padding: 2rem;
            transition: background 0.18s;
        }
        .feature-card:hover { background: var(--surface-2); }
        .feature-icon {
            width: 44px; height: 44px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            background: rgba(29,156,240,0.1); border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .feature-card h3 {
            font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .feature-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }

        /* ── AUDIENCE SPLIT ── */
        .audience-grid {
            margin-top: 3.5rem;
            display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) { .audience-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
        .audience-card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: 2.5rem;
        }
        .audience-card.highlight { border-color: rgba(29,156,240,0.3); }
        .audience-card h3 {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .audience-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
        .audience-list li {
            display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted);
        }
        .audience-list li::before {
            content: '';
            width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--accent); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 7px;
        }
        .audience-label {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
            font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase; padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }
        .label-public { background: rgba(34,197,94,0.1); color: var(--green); }
        .label-concess { background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1); color: var(--amber); }

        /* ── DASHBOARD PREVIEW ── */
        .preview-wrap {
            margin-top: 3.5rem;
            border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
            overflow: hidden; background: var(--surface);
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .preview-bar {
            display: flex; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .preview-dot { width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%; }
        .dot-red   { background: var(--red); }
        .dot-amber { background: var(--amber); }
        .dot-green { background: var(--green); }
        .preview-kpis {
            display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .kpi-box {
            background: var(--surface-2); border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius-md); padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
        }
        .kpi-val { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 800; }
        .kpi-lbl { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }
        .kpi-val.green { color: var(--green); }
        .kpi-val.amber { color: var(--amber); }
        .kpi-val.red   { color: var(--red); }
        .kpi-val.blue  { color: var(--accent); }
        .preview-map {
            height: 220px; border-radius: var(--radius-md);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d1b2a 0%, #112233 50%, #0d1b2a 100%);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .map-grid {
            position: absolute; inset: 0;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(29,156,240,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(29,156,240,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
        }
        .map-road-h {
            position: absolute; left: 0; right: 0;
            height: 3px; background: rgba(29,156,240,0.25);
        }
        .map-road-v {
            position: absolute; top: 0; bottom: 0;
            width: 3px; background: rgba(29,156,240,0.2);
        }
        .map-alert {
            position: absolute;
            width: 12px; height: 12px; border-radius: 50%;
            animation: blink 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes blink { 0%,100%{transform:scale(1);opacity:1} 50%{transform:scale(1.5);opacity:0.6} }
        .map-label {
            position: relative; z-index: 2;
            font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--muted);
        }

        /* ── CTA SECTION ── */
        .cta-section {
            background: var(--surface);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            text-align: center;
        }
        .cta-section h2 {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem);
            font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .cta-section p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .cta-actions { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--faint);
        }
        .contact-info a { color: var(--muted); transition: color 0.18s; }
        .contact-info a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

        /* ── FOOTER ── */
        footer {
            padding: 2.5rem clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
            flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 1rem;
        }
        footer p { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--faint); }
        .footer-login {
            font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted);
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
        }
        .footer-login a {
            color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600;
            transition: color 0.18s;
        }
        .footer-login a:hover { color: #fff; }

        /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .hero-actions { flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
            .btn-primary, .btn-ghost { width: 100%; max-width: 320px; text-align: center; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
        <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 28 28" fill="none">
            <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="13" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
            <path d="M8 14c0-3.314 2.686-6 6-6s6 2.686 6 6-2.686 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
            <circle cx="14" cy="14" r="3" fill="currentColor"/>
            <path d="M14 8v2M14 18v2M8 14H6M22 14h-2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
        WazeBR
    </a>
    <a href="{{ path('auth_login') }}" class="nav-cta">Acessar plataforma</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-glow"></div>
    <div class="hero-badge"><span></span> Plataforma ativa em tempo real</div>
    <h1>Monitoramento de tráfego<br>para <em>gestão pública</em> e rodovias</h1>
    <p>Centralize alertas do Waze, congestionamentos, dados pluviométricos e eventos de tráfego em um único dashboard operacional para sua equipe.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="mailto:contato@wazebr.com.br" class="btn-primary">Solicitar demonstração</a>
        <a href="#funcionalidades" class="btn-ghost">Ver funcionalidades</a>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stats-grid">
        <div>
            <div class="stat-val">24/7</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Coleta contínua de dados</div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div class="stat-val">&lt; 5min</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Latência de atualização</div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div class="stat-val">100+</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Tipos de alertas Waze</div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div class="stat-val">Multi</div>
            <div class="stat-label">Regiões simultâneas</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- FUNCIONALIDADES -->
<section id="funcionalidades">
    <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-tag">Funcionalidades</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Tudo que sua operação precisa<br>em um só lugar</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Dados do Waze processados e organizados para decisões rápidas no campo e na sala de operações.</p>

        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Alertas em tempo real</h3>
                <p>Acidentes, obras, radares, pontos de alagamento e ocorrências policiais capturados diretamente da API Waze e classificados automaticamente.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Monitoramento de congestionamentos</h3>
                <p>Nível de tráfego, velocidade média, comprimento e tempo de atraso por trecho monitorado, com histórico e gráficos por hora.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20 17.58A5 5 0 0018 8h-1.26A8 8 0 104 16.25"/><line x1="8" y1="16" x2="8.01" y2="16"/><line x1="8" y1="20" x2="8.01" y2="20"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/><line x1="12" y1="22" x2="12.01" y2="22"/><line x1="16" y1="16" x2="16.01" y2="16"/><line x1="16" y1="20" x2="16.01" y2="20"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Dados pluviométricos CEMADEN</h3>
                <p>Integração com a rede de pluviômetros do CEMADEN para correlacionar chuvas com ocorrências de tráfego e pontos de risco.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Gestão multi-parceiro</h3>
                <p>Cada órgão ou concessionária tem seu próprio ambiente isolado com cidades, rotas e configurações independentes.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/><line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Dashboard operacional</h3>
                <p>Visão consolidada com KPIs, mapa interativo, gráficos de distribuição e listagem de eventos recentes atualizada automaticamente.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 010 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 01-4 4H6a4 4 0 01-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>API para integração externa</h3>
                <p>Endpoints REST para integrar com sistemas de CCO, painéis de mensagens variáveis (PMV) e outros sistemas legados municipais.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- PÚBLICO-ALVO -->
<section id="publico" style="background: var(--surface); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
    <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-tag">Para quem é</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Desenvolvido para quem<br>opera no campo</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Solução pensada para os dois principais perfis que gerenciam tráfego urbano e rodoviário no Brasil.</p>

        <div class="audience-grid">
            <div class="audience-card highlight">
                <span class="audience-label label-public">🏛 Órgãos Públicos</span>
                <h3>Prefeituras &amp; Secretarias de Trânsito</h3>
                <ul class="audience-list">
                    <li>CET, SMTT, BHTRANS e similares</li>
                    <li>Salas de controle e operações (CCO)</li>
                    <li>Monitoramento de vias urbanas e marginais</li>
                    <li>Correlação de ocorrências com eventos de chuva</li>
                    <li>Suporte a decisões de desvio e interdição</li>
                    <li>Integração com sistemas públicos de alerta</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="audience-card">
                <span class="audience-label label-concess">🛣 Concessionárias</span>
                <h3>Rodovias Federais &amp; Estaduais</h3>
                <ul class="audience-list">
                    <li>Monitoramento de trechos concedidos</li>
                    <li>Alertas de acidentes e bloqueios em tempo real</li>
                    <li>Controle de rotas alternativas e desvios</li>
                    <li>Envio de dados para PMV e aplicativos de rota</li>
                    <li>Relatórios de ocorrências para fiscalização</li>
                    <li>API CIFS para publicação no Waze Editor</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- PREVIEW DO DASHBOARD -->
<section id="preview">
    <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="section-tag">Interface</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Dashboard pensado para<br>operações 24 horas</h2>
        <p class="section-sub">Visão imediata dos indicadores críticos sem precisar navegar entre telas.</p>

        <div class="preview-wrap">
            <div class="preview-bar">
                <div class="preview-dot dot-red"></div>
                <div class="preview-dot dot-amber"></div>
                <div class="preview-dot dot-green"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="preview-kpis">
                <div class="kpi-box">
                    <div class="kpi-val blue">247</div>
                    <div class="kpi-lbl">Alertas (24h)</div>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-box">
                    <div class="kpi-val amber">38</div>
                    <div class="kpi-lbl">Jams ativos</div>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-box">
                    <div class="kpi-val red">Nível 4</div>
                    <div class="kpi-lbl">Pior congestionamento</div>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-box">
                    <div class="kpi-val green">18 km/h</div>
                    <div class="kpi-lbl">Velocidade média</div>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-box">
                    <div class="kpi-val blue">12,4mm</div>
                    <div class="kpi-lbl">Chuva última hora</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="preview-map">
